Privacy Policy
Introduction
Our company creates and releases mobile applications. When we refer to "we," "our," or "us" in this Privacy Policy, we are referring to our company. This Privacy Policy is applicable whenever you utilize any of our Services, including our apps, or other products and services. By using any of our Services, including accessing them via mobile devices or social networks, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy and acknowledge that we will collect and utilize your information in accordance with the provisions of this Policy.
Information We Collect Automatically
The Applications may automatically gather certain information, such as the type of mobile device you are using, your mobile operating system, and details regarding how you utilize the Application. This information is collected automatically and may not be limited to what is mentioned above.
If you access our Services through AppsStone or a social network, you may choose to provide us with information directly. We will store the information you provide us on our systems and use it for the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy.
Data Security
We are dedicated to safeguarding your information and employ suitable security measures to protect it, whether it is stored online or offline. We take the security of customer information very seriously, and as such, we are committed to ensuring that your data is treated securely and in compliance with this Privacy Policy. We will take reasonable measures to ensure the protection of your information.
Changes
We reserve the right to amend this Privacy Policy at any time, and we suggest that you review it on a regular basis. Please check this privacy page periodically to stay informed of any changes. By continuing to use our Services, you acknowledge and accept any modifications made to this Privacy Policy.
